msgstr "ສະບາຍດີ!"

#. module: industry_restaurant
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:industry_restaurant.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If bundling tables for larger groups is a common practice at your place, you"
" can setup such configuration by defining which tables can be added to one "
"by opening a tabe and assigning linled resources: Appointments App &gt; "
"Configuration &gt; Resources &gt; Select the table to link others to."
msgstr ""
"ຫາກການຕໍ່ໂຕະສຳລັບກຸ່ມໃຫຍ່ເປັນເລື່ອງປົກກະຕິໃນຮ້ານຂອງທ່ານ, ທ່ານສາມາດຕັ້ງຄ່າໄດ້ໂດຍການກຳນົດວ່າໂຕະໃດສາ"
"ມາດຕໍ່ເຂົ້າກັນໄດ້: ແອັບນັດໝາຍ &gt; ການກຳນົດຄ່າ &gt; ຊັບພະຍາກອນ &gt; ເລືອກໂຕະເພື່ອເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ກັບໂຕະ"
"ອື່ນ."

#. module: industry_restaurant
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:industry_restaurant.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If you navigate to your <strong>Purchase App</strong>, you can see a new "
"Purchase Order that is ready to be sent. You can choose a packaging if your "
"product has an existing one."
msgstr ""
"ຫາກທ່ານໄປທີ່ <strong>ແອັບການຈັດຊື້</strong>, ທ່ານຈະເຫັນໃບສັ່ງຊື້ໃໝ່ທີ່ພ້ອມຈະສົ່ງ. ທ່ານສາມາດເລືອກຮູບ"
"ແບບການບັນຈຸພັນໄດ້ ຫາກສິນຄ້າຂອງທ່ານມີການຕັ້ງຄ່າໄວ້."

#. module: industry_restaurant
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:industry_restaurant.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If you want each employee to have their own access as users, you will need "
